Mix dry ingredients in blender w/ dough hook. Add water slowly.  Knead 2-3 minutes. Roll out to 1/4" thickeness and cut into
1.66 oz. Servings (see below).  Fry each piece in deep fryer till golden brown.  Keep warmed in oven.
Use #30 scoop for 1 serving, or weigh out on digital scale to .1#, or use oz scale @ 1 2/3 oz.  Makes 192 pieces
One serving is one piece as weighed out (pre-frying) above.
One piece provides 2 servings B grain, or 31.25 grams creditable grain per serving.
